1.0.0
Initial "public" release.  The following features are implemented:
    - Login with LDAP
    - 3 different perimissions are available:
        * admin
        * edit (which everyone gets upon intitial login)
        * keyword
    - Basic URL shortening/redirect
    - keyword (with permission) shortcuts
    - viewing all links you have created
    - Editing an existing link
    - Basic reporting
        * Date link is created
        * Date link was last accessed
        * Total hits for a link
    - Help information
